ap-SJ-G3055M-1.png","https://seajong.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Ga-thoat-san-SUS304-cao-cap-SJ-G3055M-2.png","https://seajong.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Ga-thoat-san-SUS304-cao-cap-SJ-G3055M-3.png","https://seajong.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Ga-thoat-san-SUS304-cao-cap-SJ-G3055M-4.png","https://seajong.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Ga-thoat-san-SUS304-cao-cap-SJ-G3055M-9.png","https://seajong.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Ga-thoat-san-SUS304-cao-cap-SJ-G3055M-10.png","https://seajong.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Ga-thoat-san-SUS304-cao-cap-SJ-G3055M-11.png","https://seajong.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Ga-thoat-san-SUS304-cao-cap-SJ-G3055M-12.png","https://seajong.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Ga-thoat-san-SUS304-cao-cap-SJ-G3055M-13.png"]','{"Mã sản phẩm:":"SJ-G3055M","Kiểu dáng:":"Thoát sàn mặt nan dài","Kích thước (mm):":"300x55x125mm","Kích thước lỗ thoát:":"Ø50mm / Ø60mm","Độ dày (mm):":"3mm","Chất liệu:":"Inox SUS 304 (Posco Hàn Quốc)","Bề mặt:":"Chải Hairline","Chiều dài":"3000","Chiều cao":"125mm","Chiều rộng":"55","Thời gian bảo hành":"10 Năm"}',1250000.0,1780823652000,1782619230872,'https://seajong.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/SJ-G3055M.webp');
